i chose this 5 star rating, because i like this one to, and it is very interesting, how these people study these tornados in the midwest in different areas that are very flat with no mountains at all.  i would not want to live in the midwest since they have a lot of problems with tornados.  i recommend this movie to everyone that likes tornados.
Very cool show -- it was on National Geographic channel.  The tornadoes are wild!
My kiddo loves tornadoes, so he has watched this DVD dozens of times.  It has kept him entertained for hours.
